<D>__{bring it back here when you find it!}
<A>__{carl rolls his eyes and begins to close his door. he stops short. a large truck is backing up, getting dangerously close to ellie's mailbox.}
<C>__{construction worker steve}
<D>__{okay, keep her coming... and... stop. stop! stop!!}
