<D>__{i don't want you to touch it!}
<A>__{carl hits the worker with his cane. he falls to the sidewalk. the worker rubs his head. blood. carl backs up toward his door, cradling his mailbox. what has he done? passerbys stare. workers gather, as does the real estate developer. carl backs into his house.}
